### Generate logistics events
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/generate?count=100&type=logistics

### Generate ledger events
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/generate?count=100&type=ledger

### Dry-run publish
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/publish?target=auto&dryRun=true

### Publish only Archive-Logistics target events
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/publish?target=logitics

### Publish only Archive-Ledger target events
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/publish?target=ledger

### Outbox summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/summary

### Integration summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/integrations/summary

### Nexus economy summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nexus-economy/summary

### Receive synthetic Archive-Logistics fee
POST http://localhost:8080/api/economy/events/external
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "LOG-FEE-20260709-000001",
  "idempotencyKey": "Archive-Logistics:LOGISTICS_SERVICE_FEE_PAID:LOG-FEE-20260709-000001",
  "simulationRunId": "SIM-DEMO-001",
  "settlementCycleId": "CYCLE-20260709",
  "correlationId": "corr-demo-001",
  "causationId": "route-cost-001",
  "hopCount": 1,
  "maxHop": 8,
  "sourceService": "Archive-Logistics",
  "costType": "LOGISTICS_SERVICE_FEE_PAID",
  "costAmount": 125000,
  "currency": "KRW",
  "reason": "Synthetic logistics service fee billed to Nexus"
}

### Nexus daily close
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nexus-economy/daily-close?date=2026-07-09

### Failed events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events?status=FAILED

### Pending retry events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events?status=PENDING_RETRY

### Logistics target events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events?targetService=LOGITICS

### Ledger target events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events?targetService=LEDGER

### PowerShell examples
# curl.exe -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/generate?count=100&type=logistics"
# curl.exe -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/events/publish?target=auto&dryRun=true"
# curl.exe "http://localhost:8080/api/outbox/summary"
# curl.exe "http://localhost:8080/api/integrations/summary"
# curl.exe "http://localhost:8080/api/nexus-economy/summary"
